---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Foster Care | Homeless Hounds Animal Rescue">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-800 text-white py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Foster Care</h1>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-yellow-300 font-semibold mb-6">Give Animals a Second Chance</h2>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-8">
            Foster care saves lives. By opening your home temporarily, you help animals recover,
            heal and prepare for their forever homes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-purple-100 mb-8">
            <em>Homeless Hounds is registered as a charity with the Australian Charities and Not-for-profits Commission – ABN 93 136 291 221</em>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">

      <!-- Why Foster Section -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why should I become a foster carer?</h3>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-6">
            Foster carers are the backbone of our rescue operations. Without foster homes, we simply cannot save as many animals.
            By fostering, you're providing a safe, loving environment where animals can recover from trauma, illness, or surgery,
            and learn to trust humans again.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Many of the animals that come into our care need time to decompress and heal – something that's difficult to achieve
            in a shelter environment. Foster homes provide the peace, quiet, and individual attention these animals need to flourish.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Foster care is also incredibly rewarding. You get to witness an animal's transformation from scared and uncertain
            to confident and ready for adoption. You're literally saving lives and giving animals a second chance at happiness.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Animals Needing Help -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Animals That Need Foster Care</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Pregnant Animals</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Expecting mothers need a quiet, stress-free environment to give birth and raise their babies safely.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Mothers with Babies</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              New mothers and their offspring need a calm environment during those crucial first weeks of life.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Medical Recovery</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Animals recovering from surgery or illness need a quiet place to heal with monitoring and care.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Behavioural Rehabilitation</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Some animals need help learning to trust humans again or basic house training and socialisation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Emergency Care</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              When shelters are full or animals need immediate help, foster homes provide life-saving temporary accommodation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 pl-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Senior Animals</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Older animals often struggle in shelter environments and thrive in the comfort of a loving foster home.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Foster Care FAQ -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <div class="space-y-8">

          <!-- FAQ 1 -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">How long do animals stay in foster care?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Foster periods vary depending on the animal's needs. It could be a few weeks for a healthy animal
              waiting for adoption, several months for a mother with babies, or longer for animals requiring
              medical treatment or behavioural rehabilitation. We'll always discuss the expected timeframe with you beforehand.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 2 -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What support do foster carers receive?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Homeless Hounds covers all veterinary expenses and provides food, bedding, toys, and any other
              supplies needed. You'll have 24/7 access to our support team and experienced volunteers for advice
              and assistance. We also provide training and resources to help you succeed as a foster carer.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 3 -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">What if I fall in love with my foster animal?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Foster carers have first option to adopt their foster animals! Many of our volunteers have become
              "foster failures" – and we couldn't be happier. If you decide to adopt, you'll go through the same
              adoption process as any other applicant to ensure it's the right match.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 4 -->
          <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Do I need experience with animals to foster?</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              While experience is helpful, it's not essential. What matters most is your commitment, patience, and
              willingness to learn. We provide comprehensive support and training to all our foster carers, regardless
              of their experience level. We'll match you with animals that suit your comfort level and experience.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Application Information -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Ready to Start Fostering?</h3>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 mb-8">
          <p class="mb-4">
            If you're ready to make a difference in an animal's life, we'd love to hear from you.
            The application process helps us understand your living situation, experience, and preferences
            so we can match you with the right animals.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            We have separate application processes for dog and cat foster carers, as the requirements
            and considerations can be different for each type of animal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Current Application Note -->
        <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-amber-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-amber-700">
                <strong>Foster applications are currently being updated.</strong>
                Please <a href="/contact-us" class="underline text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">contact us directly</a>
                if you're interested in becoming a foster carer and we'll guide you through the application process.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-900 mb-4">Get Started Today</h4>
          <p class="text-purple-800 mb-4">
            Ready to open your heart and home to an animal in need? Contact us to begin your foster care journey:
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="/contact-us"
               class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-700 transition-colors text-center">
              Contact Us
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:info@homelesshounds.com.au"
               class="inline-block bg-white text-purple-600 border-2 border-purple-600 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors text-center">
              Email Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What We Provide -->
      <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What Homeless Hounds Provides</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Medical Care</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                All veterinary expenses covered
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Regular health checks and vaccinations
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Emergency medical care when needed
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Desexing before adoption
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Supplies & Support</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Food and bedding provided
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Toys and enrichment items
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                24/7 support from our team
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Training and guidance throughout
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-800 rounded-lg text-white p-8 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Every Animal Deserves Love</h3>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Your foster home could be the bridge between an animal's difficult past and their bright future.
          Together, we can save more lives.
        </p>
        <p class="text-purple-200">
          Foster care: where healing begins and hope is restored.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Base>